title: Coronavirus: Cotton On Group closes stores nationwide

content:
Iconic Aussie brand Cotton On has made the decision to close its doors nationwide.“From 5pm Sunday 29 March, all our AUS stores will be temporarily closed,” the brand notified customers via social media.
